    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300075719_56_10388-10460",
      "chapterUid": 56,
      "range": "10388-10460",
      "markText": "要解释中产阶级子弟为何从事中产阶级工作，难点在于解释别人为什么成全他们。要解释工人阶级子弟为何从事工人阶级工作，难点却是解释他们为什么自甘如此。",
      "totalCount": 306,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300075719&chapterUid=56&rangeStart=10388&rangeEnd=10460",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8fb32e90813ab8413g019b41?chapterUid=56&rangeStart=10388&rangeEnd=10460"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300075719_48_1715-1797",
      "chapterUid": 48,
      "range": "1715-1797",
      "markText": "但需要认识到的是，当社会发生结构性的病变，个人英雄主义式的努力就显得渺小和无力。农家子弟身上自带的天分、不屈的勇气和激昂的道德力量，高度依赖一个健全的公共支持体系。",
      "totalCount": 286,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300075719&chapterUid=48&rangeStart=1715&rangeEnd=1797",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8fb32e90813ab8413g019b41?chapterUid=48&rangeStart=1715&rangeEnd=1797"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300075719_55_1194-1219",
      "chapterUid": 55,
      "range": "1194-1219",
      "markText": "三只牛吃草。一只羊也吃草。一只羊不吃草，他看着花。",
      "totalCount": 270,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300075719&chapterUid=55&rangeStart=1194&rangeEnd=1219",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8fb32e90813ab8413g019b41?chapterUid=55&rangeStart=1194&rangeEnd=1219"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300075719_57_2474-2527",
      "chapterUid": 57,
      "range": "2474-2527",
      "markText": "我曾一次次地问自己：为什么偏偏就我生在农村，就该忍受贫穷的牢笼，就该付出更多的努力才能获得向上发展的空间？",
      "totalCount": 256,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300075719&chapterUid=57&rangeStart=2474&rangeEnd=2527",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8fb32e90813ab8413g019b41?chapterUid=57&rangeStart=2474&rangeEnd=2527"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300075719_52_1997-2060",
      "chapterUid": 52,
      "range": "1997-2060",
      "markText": "高学业成就的农家子弟并不会、也不可能完全割舍与原生家庭的文化连接，而是在情感上与家人爱怨交织，在行动中创造性地重建着家人关系。",
      "totalCount": 255,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300075719&chapterUid=52&rangeStart=1997&rangeEnd=2060",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8fb32e90813ab8413g019b41?chapterUid=52&rangeStart=1997&rangeEnd=2060"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300075719_57_2321-2344",
      "chapterUid": 57,
      "range": "2321-2344",
      "markText": "与生存相比，自尊心只是累赘，却又是唯一的倚靠。",
      "totalCount": 255,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300075719&chapterUid=57&rangeStart=2321&rangeEnd=2344",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8fb32e90813ab8413g019b41?chapterUid=57&rangeStart=2321&rangeEnd=2344"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300075719_52_1093-1142",
      "chapterUid": 52,
      "range": "1093-1142",
      "markText": "农家子弟取得高学业成就的关键不在于其弥补了自身文化资本的缺陷，而是充分利用底层特有文化资本的结果。",
      "totalCount": 238,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300075719&chapterUid=52&rangeStart=1093&rangeEnd=1142",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8fb32e90813ab8413g019b41?chapterUid=52&rangeStart=1093&rangeEnd=1142"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300075719_66_9029-9086",
      "chapterUid": 66,
      "range": "9029-9086",
      "markText": "农民的苦难不是无来由的。在长期实行重城市、轻农村的发展战略下，国家通过工农产品的不等价交换完成了工业化的原始积累。",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300075719&chapterUid=66&rangeStart=9029&rangeEnd=9086",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8fb32e90813ab8413g019b41?chapterUid=66&rangeStart=9029&rangeEnd=9086"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300075719_52_1440-1524",
      "chapterUid": 52,
      "range": "1440-1524",
      "markText": "“读书的料”取得高学业成就的另一代价是基于个人苦修之上的片面发展，引发严重的成功焦虑，承受贤能主义的竞争风险，陷入异化与自我疏离的困扰，甚至走向成功与幸福相对立的道路。",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300075719&chapterUid=52&rangeStart=1440&rangeEnd=1524",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8fb32e90813ab8413g019b41?chapterUid=52&rangeStart=1440&rangeEnd=1524"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300075719_57_4827-4886",
      "chapterUid": 57,
      "range": "4827-4886",
      "markText": "有的时候，以为农村背景是失败者的耻辱、蛰伏着的隐痛，是成功的陪衬品，是从深海向水面上浮时需要慢慢抛掉的融入血液的气泡。",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300075719&chapterUid=57&rangeStart=4827&rangeEnd=4886",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8fb32e90813ab8413g019b41?chapterUid=57&rangeStart=4827&rangeEnd=4886"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300075719_54_1354-1420",
      "chapterUid": 54,
      "range": "1354-1420",
      "markText": "在凌乱的写作过程中，我时常找不到感觉，那些我厌恶的虚妄、空洞、陌生、矫情灌满了每一个字。更让我焦虑和厌恶的是，我只能写出这样的文字。",
      "totalCount": 209,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300075719&chapterUid=54&rangeStart=1354&rangeEnd=1420",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8fb32e90813ab8413g019b41?chapterUid=54&rangeStart=1354&rangeEnd=1420"
